        <hl1>Gore's Style of Debate</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Al Gore, who has appeared in 43 televised debates in his political career, has a reputation as a combative opponent. His style might be summed up by this advice from his mother: ''Smile, relax, attack.''</p>
        <p>Article, Page A23.</p>
